            passionate writers. Your next great story starts here.
          </p>
          <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start">
            <a href="/blog"
              ><button
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-lg px-4 me-md-2 btn-head"
                style="background-color: #7645d8; color: white"
              >
                Start Blogging
              </button></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="blog-div">
      <h1 class="section-heading">Explore Your Next Favorite Read</h1>
      <div class="container-blog">
        <div>
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Food Blog</h2>
            <span>Savor the flavors of life</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="content">
